## Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Laravel 13.2.0 (PHP 8.4.20)
- **Frontend**: Vue 3 + Vite 8 + Pinia + Vue Router
- **Database**: MySQL 8.4 (via Laravel Sail)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4
- **Cache**: Redis (via Laravel Sail)
- **Testing**: PHPUnit 12 (unit/feature) + Playwright (E2E)

