## Available Scripts

### Backend (via Laravel Sail)
```bash
./vendor/bin/sail up -d                    # Start all Docker services
./vendor/bin/sail artisan migrate:fresh --seed  # Reset + seed DB
./vendor/bin/sail artisan test             # Run all tests
./vendor/bin/sail artisan queue:work       # Process job queue
./vendor/bin/sail artisan make:model X -m  # Create model + migration
./vendor/bin/sail artisan make:controller X --resource
```

### Frontend
```bash
npm run dev              # Vite dev server (port 5174)
npm run build            # Production build
npm run test:e2e         # Playwright E2E tests
npm run test:e2e:ui      # Playwright UI mode
```

## Database (MySQL via Docker)
