## Common Dev Workflow
```bash
# Start everything
./vendor/bin/sail up -d
npm run dev

# After pulling changes
composer install
./vendor/bin/sail artisan migrate

# Reset and seed
./vendor/bin/sail artisan migrate:fresh --seed

# Run tests
./vendor/bin/sail artisan test --parallel
npm run test:e2e
```
